in his later film career , he appeared in inherit the wind ( 1960 ) ; how the west was won ( 1962 ) ( as ulysses s. grant ) ; john goldfarb , please come home ( 1965 ) ; frankie and johnny ( 1966 ) ; support your local sheriff ! ( 1969 ) ; support your local gunfighter ! ( 1971 ) ; snowball express ( 1972 ) ; the shootist ( 1976 ) ; the wild wild west revisited ( 1979 ) ; and as captain gannon in the film version of dragnet ( 1987 ) with dan aykroyd and tom hanks .

